    <h2>Head Coach - Tim Kersey</h2>
    <p>
        Since the Fall of 2013 Tim has been the Head Cross Country Coach at Como Park Senior High. Born and raised in St. Anthony Park, Tim is a 1993 graduate of St. Paul Central High School. He studied Physiological Sciences and graduated in 1998 with a BS in Health Sciences from the University of Arizona where he played hockey for the Arizona Icecats. 
Tim has worked as a personal trainer at Shoreview Community Center over the past 11 years, conducting personal fitness training, employee training, and developing the Center’s fitness assessment program.Tim is the founder and president of Minnesota Exercise Professionals, LLC.
    </p>
    <h3>COACHING EXPERIENCE</h3>
