    <h2>Assistant Coach - Jim Rue</h2>
    <p>
        Jim Rue joined the Como Park Senior High cross country team as an assistant coach in the Fall of 2016.
    He is an avid runner, having completed many local short and long distance races including the Twin Cities Marathon.
    His coaching goal is to help each student enjoy the sport, learn how to run effectively, efficiently, and injury-free.
    </p>
    <h3>Background</h3>
    <p>
        Coach Rue graduated with a degree in Sociology from the University of Minnesota and a Master’s degree in Special Education from the
